1
00:00:21,070 --> 00:00:24,180
♪The breeze of the 1990s drifts by♪

2
00:00:24,350 --> 00:00:27,180
♪Memories slowly flicker past♪

3
00:00:27,650 --> 00:00:31,430
♪My heartbeat
rises and falls with the tune♪

4
00:00:31,500 --> 00:00:34,580
♪The story quietly begins here♪

5
00:00:35,330 --> 00:00:38,640
♪Under the dim lights, our eyes meet♪

6
00:00:38,710 --> 00:00:41,850
♪Time seems to stand still♪

7
00:00:42,350 --> 00:00:45,990
♪Your smile
breaks through the clouds like sun♪

8
00:00:46,060 --> 00:00:49,150
♪Melting the snow deep in my heart♪

9
00:00:49,580 --> 00:00:53,090
♪Street posters spread signals of love♪

10
00:00:53,150 --> 00:00:56,110
♪Our story slowly begins to ferment♪

11
00:00:56,800 --> 00:01:00,730
♪Hand in hand,
going through every dusk corner♪

12
00:01:00,930 --> 00:01:04,800
♪The taste of happiness is so subtle♪

13
00:01:05,480 --> 00:01:08,740
♪Crossing back to the 1990s stage♪

14
00:01:09,150 --> 00:01:12,480
♪You're my most beautiful surprise♪

15
00:01:12,790 --> 00:01:16,210
♪Love's flame burns within my heart♪

16
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:19,710
♪Not afraid of obstacles ahead♪

17
00:01:20,180 --> 00:01:23,560
♪Sway with the rhythm.
Feel your heart pound♪

18
00:01:23,660 --> 00:01:27,150
♪This love will never change♪

19
00:01:27,950 --> 00:01:35,080
♪We hold tight in this crazy era♪

20
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:40,060
♪1990s love is what we rely on♪

21
00:01:40,100 --> 00:01:42,070
=Once More Love in 1995=

22
00:01:42,260 --> 00:01:44,950
=Episode 19=

23
00:01:49,362 --> 00:01:50,162
Long.

24
00:01:50,522 --> 00:01:51,321
Long.

25
00:01:51,802 --> 00:01:52,962
Zhou.

26
00:01:53,962 --> 00:01:55,401
When we face a problem,

27
00:01:55,975 --> 00:01:57,415
we solve it.

28
00:02:02,802 --> 00:02:04,002
Why are you dodging?

29
00:02:05,737 --> 00:02:06,377
Long.

30
00:02:07,242 --> 00:02:07,761
I swear,

31
00:02:07,761 --> 00:02:09,975
I had no idea
how Qin Mo got connected to Malaysia.

32
00:02:10,202 --> 00:02:12,362
When I was at Jinxin,
they had no business ties at all.

33
00:02:14,762 --> 00:02:15,482
It's a trap.

34
00:02:15,762 --> 00:02:16,802
Yes, Long.

35
00:02:17,161 --> 00:02:18,681
This has to be a trap, Long.

36
00:02:19,202 --> 00:02:20,441
A trap?

37
00:02:21,281 --> 00:02:22,401
Yes. Otherwise,

38
00:02:22,522 --> 00:02:23,681
how could they

39
00:02:23,775 --> 00:02:25,255
lock in that supply so fast?

40
00:02:25,601 --> 00:02:26,401
Let me tell you

41
00:02:26,401 --> 00:02:27,762
what a trap really is.

42
00:02:29,100 --> 00:02:29,459
Long.

43
00:02:29,681 --> 00:02:31,082
I'll tell you what a trap is.

44
00:02:31,082 --> 00:02:31,802
A trap

45
00:02:31,802 --> 00:02:34,202
is how I risk my entire fortune
digging a pit with you,

46
00:02:34,522 --> 00:02:36,561
yet Qin Mo fixes it
with a snap of his fingers.

47
00:02:36,802 --> 00:02:38,242
My warehouse

48
00:02:38,242 --> 00:02:39,642
is now stacked with palm oil

49
00:02:39,642 --> 00:02:42,202
that won't sell and ruined me!

50
00:02:42,202 --> 00:02:43,762
What do you think I should do?

51
00:02:43,762 --> 00:02:44,962
What should I do?

52
00:02:45,001 --> 00:02:47,082
What should I do?

53
00:02:59,202 --> 00:03:00,242
Zhou Zeyang.

54
00:03:00,242 --> 00:03:01,762
When I stole Qin Mo's order,

55
00:03:01,762 --> 00:03:03,082
what did you tell me?

56
00:03:03,362 --> 00:03:06,482
You said he wouldn't find
a supplier anytime soon.

57
00:03:06,482 --> 00:03:07,922
Once Jinxin's production stopped,

58
00:03:07,922 --> 00:03:09,922
I could sell this palm oil
at sky high prices

59
00:03:09,922 --> 00:03:11,802
and watch Qin Mo go bankrupt.

60
00:03:11,962 --> 00:03:13,121
Now what?

61
00:03:13,482 --> 00:03:14,762
Now what?

62
00:03:14,762 --> 00:03:16,121
I lifted a rock

63
00:03:16,121 --> 00:03:17,242
and smashed my own foot.

64
00:03:17,482 --> 00:03:18,522
I smashed my own foot.

65
00:03:24,281 --> 00:03:25,721
Do I, Zhang Guolong,

66
00:03:26,675 --> 00:03:28,715
look like a sucker to you?

67
00:03:29,275 --> 00:03:30,275
Huh?

68
00:03:31,721 --> 00:03:32,522
Long.

69
00:03:33,642 --> 00:03:35,281
Long.

70
00:03:35,322 --> 00:03:37,522
Long, give me a bit more time.

71
00:03:37,522 --> 00:03:38,881
I'll fix this.

72
00:03:39,242 --> 00:03:41,642
I won't let you lose money, Long.

73
00:03:47,401 --> 00:03:49,762
Right now, your face

74
00:03:49,762 --> 00:03:52,082
is the only thing still useful.

75
00:03:55,601 --> 00:03:59,721
I don't care if you hook up
with the one surnamed Qin or Zhuang.

76
00:03:59,962 --> 00:04:03,202
You must sell that palm oil
at the original price.

77
00:04:06,482 --> 00:04:09,322
Otherwise, I'll take your life.

78
00:04:11,161 --> 00:04:12,121
Do you understand?

79
00:04:14,161 --> 00:04:15,762
Did you hear me?

80
00:04:15,762 --> 00:04:16,202
Yes.

81
00:04:16,202 --> 00:04:17,562
I heard you clearly, Long.

82
00:04:26,002 --> 00:04:26,762
Jiamin.

83
00:04:27,122 --> 00:04:28,002
Jiamin.

84
00:04:28,002 --> 00:04:30,562
Jiamin, I'm sorry. I was wrong.

85
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:31,962
What are you talking about?

86
00:04:32,250 --> 00:04:33,649
I took

87
00:04:34,762 --> 00:04:36,481
that palm oil order.

88
00:04:36,882 --> 00:04:38,481
Zhang Guolong ran back to Haicheng.

89
00:04:39,237 --> 00:04:41,597
He forced me to help him
make a comeback.

90
00:04:42,841 --> 00:04:43,882
I was afraid he'd hurt you

91
00:04:43,882 --> 00:04:45,442
if I refused, Jiamin.

92
00:04:46,082 --> 00:04:47,082
I had no choice.

93
00:04:47,082 --> 00:04:49,002
I had to steal that order.

94
00:04:49,562 --> 00:04:50,481
Zhou Zeyang.

95
00:04:51,161 --> 00:04:52,642
Can I still believe you?

96
00:04:53,202 --> 00:04:55,041
I'm telling the truth, Jiamin.

97
00:04:55,041 --> 00:04:56,361
I'm telling the truth.

98
00:04:56,361 --> 00:04:57,762
I know I was wrong.

99
00:04:57,880 --> 00:04:58,962
After Jinxin got in trouble,

100
00:04:58,962 --> 00:05:01,241
I've been blaming myself nonstop.

101
00:05:01,522 --> 00:05:02,921
I wanted to tell you the truth,

102
00:05:02,921 --> 00:05:03,962
but I didn't dare.

103
00:05:03,962 --> 00:05:06,161
I was afraid you'd leave me, Jiamin.

104
00:05:10,562 --> 00:05:11,562
So what now?

105
00:05:12,082 --> 00:05:13,990
What do you want me
to help you with this time?

106
00:05:14,161 --> 00:05:14,962
Jiamin.

107
00:05:15,682 --> 00:05:16,962
Can you ask Qin Mo

108
00:05:17,601 --> 00:05:19,241
to buy Zhang Guolong's order?

109
00:05:20,562 --> 00:05:22,361
Zhang Guolong is a lunatic.

110
00:05:22,601 --> 00:05:23,762
If he loses everything,

111
00:05:23,762 --> 00:05:25,162
he will kill me!

112
00:05:25,882 --> 00:05:26,522
Jiamin.

113
00:05:27,522 --> 00:05:29,601
You won't just let me die, right?

114
00:05:30,002 --> 00:05:31,522
Qin Mo won't agree.

115
00:05:31,841 --> 00:05:32,500
I told you.

116
00:05:32,500 --> 00:05:34,281
He no longer acknowledges me
as his sister.

117
00:05:36,841 --> 00:05:37,801
Qin Jiamin.

118
00:05:38,082 --> 00:05:40,241
I have nothing left.

119
00:05:40,401 --> 00:05:42,281
You're not leaving me a way out?

120
00:05:43,642 --> 00:05:45,801
Then we'll die together.

121
00:05:46,002 --> 00:05:47,041
Do you agree or not?

122
00:05:49,642 --> 00:05:50,642
I agree.

123
00:05:51,642 --> 00:05:53,041
I agree.

124
00:05:57,281 --> 00:05:58,642
Jiamin.

125
00:05:59,522 --> 00:06:01,281
I'm sorry, Jiamin. I deserve to die.

126
00:06:01,281 --> 00:06:03,202
I deserve to die. I'm sorry, Jiamin.

127
00:06:03,202 --> 00:06:04,801
I'm sorry, Jiamin.

128
00:06:05,322 --> 00:06:06,882
I knew you wouldn't abandon me.

129
00:06:07,682 --> 00:06:09,082
Right, Jiamin?

130
00:06:09,721 --> 00:06:11,082
I can try to help.

131
00:06:11,801 --> 00:06:13,241
But even if Qin Mo agrees,

132
00:06:13,642 --> 00:06:15,082
he won't buy at the original price.

133
00:06:15,481 --> 00:06:16,642
It's fine.

134
00:06:16,801 --> 00:06:18,002
I'll make up the difference.

135
00:06:18,361 --> 00:06:20,002
As long as this batch sells,

136
00:06:20,002 --> 00:06:21,642
I can make a comeback.

137
00:06:23,442 --> 00:06:25,041
I won't let you down.

138
00:06:45,850 --> 00:06:47,412
So? Was it Qin Jiamin?

139
00:06:55,002 --> 00:06:55,801
It's fine.

140
00:06:56,401 --> 00:06:57,202
It was Jiamin.

141
00:06:58,682 --> 00:06:59,962
You scared me.

142
00:07:00,682 --> 00:07:01,361
What's going on?

143
00:07:01,522 --> 00:07:01,962
Shanshan.

144
00:07:03,082 --> 00:07:03,762
Shanshan.

145
00:07:03,962 --> 00:07:04,642
Perfect timing.

146
00:07:05,002 --> 00:07:06,361
Jiamin just called.

147
00:07:06,401 --> 00:07:08,721
Zhou Zeyang will sell
the shipment Zhang Guolong seized

148
00:07:08,721 --> 00:07:09,962
to us at a low price.

149
00:07:09,962 --> 00:07:10,750
Our crisis is over.

150
00:07:11,002 --> 00:07:12,161
Really? That's great.

151
00:07:13,002 --> 00:07:15,322
We got through this thanks to you.

152
00:07:15,841 --> 00:07:16,522
Good work.

153
00:07:21,700 --> 00:07:23,580
Congratulations to Jinxin
for escaping danger.

154
00:07:23,801 --> 00:07:25,690
And congratulations
on not losing your sister.

155
00:07:26,522 --> 00:07:29,082
Qin, you've worked hard lately.

156
00:07:30,082 --> 00:07:31,202
I made you some hot food.

157
00:07:31,202 --> 00:07:32,281
Take care of yourself.

158
00:07:35,082 --> 00:07:35,562
By the way,

159
00:07:35,841 --> 00:07:37,721
I choreographed a new dance.

160
00:07:37,721 --> 00:07:39,550
If you're free tonight,
take a look for me.

161
00:07:45,650 --> 00:07:47,218
She was saying that to you, right?

162
00:07:47,962 --> 00:07:50,601
How long will you two
use me as a shield?

163
00:07:52,481 --> 00:07:53,481
Just eat.

164
00:07:54,202 --> 00:07:55,801
You're clearly feeling guilty.

165
00:07:55,921 --> 00:07:58,322
You sisters care about each other,
but you're just stubborn.

166
00:07:58,801 --> 00:07:59,801
Sisters, indeed.

167
00:08:03,161 --> 00:08:04,361
She said it's for my health,

168
00:08:04,601 --> 00:08:06,522
but she knows
I hate sweet and sour pork.

169
00:08:06,801 --> 00:08:09,562
Who is this meal really for?

170
00:08:44,250 --> 00:08:48,887
♪Photos shelved away, old and yellowed♪

171
00:08:50,925 --> 00:08:57,262
♪Your smile stays frozen
in the year you're 29♪

172
00:08:59,225 --> 00:09:04,562
♪I press the button
to activate the time machine♪

173
00:09:05,525 --> 00:09:11,912
♪Going against the wind,
landing in a spring where you are♪

174
00:09:13,812 --> 00:09:20,050
♪Stepping onto the platform,
the whistle drowns out my heartbeat♪

175
00:09:21,062 --> 00:09:26,300
♪The winds of 1995 scatters my forecast♪

176
00:09:28,125 --> 00:09:35,387
♪I carry hatred
like a tempered steel bar♪

177
00:09:36,062 --> 00:09:42,825
♪My premonitions burst along
with its fizzy bubbles♪

178
00:09:43,287 --> 00:09:49,862
♪Time borrowed,
secretly returned to you♪

179
00:09:50,362 --> 00:09:56,650
♪Shopping for groceries with you,
going through the noisy market♪

180
00:09:58,050 --> 00:10:04,875
♪Listening to you complain
that winter melon costs more now♪

181
00:10:05,287 --> 00:10:11,350
♪Such fractured warmth
is almost beyond reach, even in dreams♪

182
00:10:13,662 --> 00:10:20,187
♪Time borrowed, closely following you♪

183
00:10:20,425 --> 00:10:26,900
♪Watching needles
weave through the afternoon♪

184
00:10:27,612 --> 00:10:31,225
♪The fine hair at your temples
glow like honey♪

185
00:10:31,282 --> 00:10:32,162
Shanshan.

186
00:10:33,521 --> 00:10:34,521
I'm sorry.

187
00:10:35,601 --> 00:10:37,881
I'm sorry too.

188
00:10:43,087 --> 00:10:49,825
♪That blue bedsheet drying in the wind♪

189
00:10:52,625 --> 00:10:56,825
♪Became the gentlest thing♪

190
00:10:58,375 --> 00:11:00,650
♪My remaining life♪

191
00:11:03,802 --> 00:11:05,180
You didn't ask her to wait for me?

192
00:11:05,761 --> 00:11:07,682
I told her you'd come out
after the meeting.

193
00:11:07,802 --> 00:11:08,562
She said

194
00:11:09,361 --> 00:11:10,162
there was no need.

195
00:11:14,425 --> 00:11:17,850
(Resignation Letter, Zhuang Yan)

196
00:11:28,562 --> 00:11:29,361
Mr. Qin.

197
00:11:30,282 --> 00:11:33,042
There are some things
I might not have the right to say,

198
00:11:33,521 --> 00:11:37,001
but if you and Ms. Zhuang
haven't said goodbye properly,

199
00:11:37,601 --> 00:11:39,361
you should find her.

200
00:11:39,922 --> 00:11:41,202
Say what needs to be said.

201
00:11:41,202 --> 00:11:42,402
Ask what needs to be asked.

202
00:11:43,001 --> 00:11:44,760
Don't separate
without a clear explanation.

203
00:11:46,322 --> 00:11:47,802
I don't know how to say goodbye.

204
00:11:48,001 --> 00:11:49,001
Just be straightforward

205
00:11:49,220 --> 00:11:50,590
that you don't want to say goodbye.

206
00:12:10,521 --> 00:12:11,322
Zhuang Yan.

207
00:12:12,601 --> 00:12:13,721
Why did you resign?

208
00:12:16,780 --> 00:12:18,521
Because I realized
everything I insisted on

209
00:12:18,521 --> 00:12:19,601
had lost its meaning.

210
00:12:20,361 --> 00:12:22,282
Shanshan and I are starting a new life.

211
00:12:22,800 --> 00:12:24,202
Then why can't I

212
00:12:24,837 --> 00:12:25,881
be in your new life?

213
00:12:34,761 --> 00:12:35,562
Zhuang Yan.

214
00:12:36,922 --> 00:12:37,962
I like you.

215
00:12:44,001 --> 00:12:44,881
I know.

216
00:12:45,922 --> 00:12:47,162
You have many secrets.

217
00:12:47,162 --> 00:12:48,481
If you don't want to share, I won't ask.

218
00:12:48,481 --> 00:12:49,562
I just want to know

219
00:12:51,162 --> 00:12:53,001
whether you feel

220
00:12:54,162 --> 00:12:55,682
the same as I do.

221
00:13:09,001 --> 00:13:10,820
You do too, right?

222
00:13:17,675 --> 00:13:18,474
Qin Mo.

223
00:13:19,775 --> 00:13:22,694
What if one day I suddenly left?

224
00:13:34,361 --> 00:13:35,521
What did you just say?

225
00:13:36,361 --> 00:13:37,682
You said you're Zhuang Manying,

226
00:13:38,402 --> 00:13:39,962
from 30 years in the future.

227
00:13:41,001 --> 00:13:42,521
Shanshan's daughter.

228
00:13:43,962 --> 00:13:44,761
Yeah.

229
00:13:49,802 --> 00:13:50,601
Zhuang Yan.

230
00:13:53,282 --> 00:13:54,682
Just to reject me,

231
00:13:55,361 --> 00:13:57,121
you came up
with such a ridiculous excuse.

232
00:14:09,601 --> 00:14:10,880
Qin Mo, have you lost your mind?

233
00:14:12,682 --> 00:14:13,601
I'm telling you.

234
00:14:14,001 --> 00:14:16,282
Whether it's 30 years later
or 300 years later,

235
00:14:16,322 --> 00:14:17,361
I'll still like you.

236
00:14:38,837 --> 00:14:42,475
♪The old dial tone circles in my ear♪

237
00:14:42,600 --> 00:14:45,912
♪Faded tickets point to a cicada summer♪

238
00:14:46,075 --> 00:14:49,662
♪The videotape
whispers your image in the frame♪

239
00:14:49,962 --> 00:14:53,250
♪Against the light, the plaid shirt
reveals a clear and transparent smile♪

240
00:14:53,475 --> 00:14:57,100
♪I'm a clumsy guest in a frozen scene♪

241
00:14:57,262 --> 00:15:00,600
♪How do I answer familiar lines?♪

242
00:15:00,675 --> 00:15:04,387
♪I know
the train will leave this station♪

243
00:15:04,437 --> 00:15:08,300
♪I know the ending's in a faded future♪

244
00:15:08,362 --> 00:15:14,412
♪Yet I want to approach that warmth♪

245
00:15:15,587 --> 00:15:22,325
♪Even one second rewrites missed lines♪

246
00:15:22,612 --> 00:15:26,887
♪Rewind to 1995,
back to the street we met♪

247
00:15:26,887 --> 00:15:30,187
♪Wind blows through the sycamore leaves
and lands on your shoulder♪

248
00:15:30,262 --> 00:15:34,562
♪I wish I could pause and stop time♪

249
00:15:34,625 --> 00:15:38,275
♪Let unspoken love
be preserved forever as amber♪

250
00:15:38,275 --> 00:15:41,837
♪Rewind to 1995,
gentle touch of fingertips♪

251
00:15:41,887 --> 00:15:45,150
♪Star sparks in your eyes burn my chest♪

252
00:15:45,150 --> 00:15:48,900
♪This looping script
is beyond my saving♪

253
00:15:48,900 --> 00:15:55,612
♪I can only stay with you till the end
in this inverted hourglass♪
